# Security headers — docs/09 §2/§4 is authoritative.
# Honoured by Cloudflare Workers Static Assets. Astro copies public/ into dist/
# verbatim, then scripts/inject-csp-hash.ts rewrites <TT_GATE_HASH> below.
#
# ⚠️ There is deliberately NO Cache-Control on the `/*` rule. Cloudflare
# APPENDS header values when several rules match a path rather than letting the
# most specific one win, so `/*` plus `/_astro/*` emitted
#
#   Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate, public, max-age=31536000, immutable
#
# — two conflicting max-age values in one header, where implementations
# generally honour the first. Every hashed bundle and the pinned font was
# therefore uncacheable: the exact opposite of docs/09 §3. Only surfaced by
# checking the live site.
#
# HTML needs no rule of its own: the Workers Static Assets default is already
# `public, max-age=0, must-revalidate`, which is what docs/09 §3 asks for.
# Setting it in the Worker is not an option either — a matching asset is served
# BEFORE the Worker runs, so worker/index.ts never sees these requests.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'sha256-<TT_GATE_HASH>' https://www.youtube.com https://www.youtube-nocookie.com; frame-src https://www.youtube-nocookie.com https://www.youtube.com; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://i.ytimg.com; media-src 'self' blob:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; font-src 'self'; connect-src 'self'; worker-src 'self' blob:; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=(), usb=(), midi=()
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY

# Only these two rules set Cache-Control, and they do not overlap each other.
# No `/*` cache rule exists, so nothing can be appended to them (see the note
# at the top of this file).
/_astro/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/fonts/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
